KDE plugins for linEAK, which provide macros for lineakd.conf. Actually, there are plugins for the following KDE applications : kscd, juk, kdesktop, kmail, kmix, and Konqueror. See /usr/share/doc/lineak_kdeplugins/README for a complete macros list.
